==In popular culture==
* In &quot;Mom and Pop Art&quot;, a 1999 episode of the animated television series &quot;The Simpsons&quot;, Johns guest-stars as himself. He is depicted as a thief who steals everyday objects such as lightbulbs. 
* In &quot;The Diplomat&quot;, a 2023 Netflix series, Johns&#x27; painting &quot;Flag&quot; is pictured hanging on the wall of the U.S. embassy in London (season 1, episodes 1 and 8).

